@startuml
title UC011 - Control Flow Diagram (Submit Car Park Review)
start

:1. User selects car park to review;
:2. Submit review request;

:3. Fetch car park data;
:4. Display review page;
:5. User enters review;
:6. Submit review;

:7. Validate review content;
if (8. Is review valid?) then (yes)
  :9. Add review to database;
  :10. Display confirmation message ("Review submitted successfully");
  stop
else (no)
  :11. Display error message ("Review content invalid");
  -5. User can edit their review
  stop
endif

@enduml
